# 🧮 Advanced BMI Calculator with GUI

A beautiful and user-friendly Body Mass Index (BMI) Calculator built using Python and Tkinter. 
This advanced version features a clean GUI, unit conversion, BMI category display, optional historical tracking, and live data visualization using Matplotlib.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🧠 **Real-Time BMI Calculation**  
  Calculate BMI using height and weight inputs, instantly categorized as Underweight, Normal, Overweight, or Obese.

- 🎨 **Aesthetic GUI**  
  Clean layout with a soothing color palette, smooth buttons, animations, and responsive design using Tkinter.

- 🔁 **Unit Converter**  
  Choose between **Metric (kg/cm)** and **Imperial (lbs/inches)** systems.

- 📈 **Historical Tracking (Optional)**  
  Store and visualize past BMI records using **Matplotlib charts**.

- 🗃️ **Data Persistence (Optional)**  
  Save data per user using **SQLite** or **JSON** for long-term tracking.

