| Tool        | Purpose                          |
|-------------|----------------------------------|
| `Python`    | Core programming language         |
| `Tkinter`   | GUI design                        |
| `Matplotlib`| Plot BMI history graph            |
| `SQLite` / `JSON` | Optional: data storage     |
| `Pillow`    | Optional: image enhancements      |

